  "6": {
    "inputs": {
      "text": "A cinematic wide shot of a vast, still freshwater pond at golden hour, the entire scene bathed in warm amber light (#FFB347) with copper-gold (#B87333) reflections shimmering across the water's surface. The western bank is sun-baked terracotta (#C75B39) clay, cracked in a fine mosaic pattern, curving gently along the pond's edge. On the eastern shore, a massive ancient banyan tree dominates the frame, its thick trunk and cascading aerial roots rendered in elephant-grey (#848484) bark draped with emerald moss (#2E8B57), the roots reaching into the water like slow fingers, copper rim light catching the textured bark. The banyan's enormous canopy casts dappled emerald shadows across the pond and bank, jade-green (#3B7A57) waxy lotus pads floating on the surface with mercury-like droplets, a single half-open lotus flower in pale pink (#FFB7C5) fading to cream catching a shaft of golden light near the center of the frame. The shallows are tawny-gold (#D4A437) and translucent, revealing smooth pebbles, decomposing leaves, and pond snail trails on the bottom, while the mysterious center deepens to dark green-brown (#2F4F2F) where the bottom vanishes. The water's surface reflects cerulean sky (#87CEEB) blending with copper-gold (#B87333) sun tones. Three dragonflies in translucent green (#76D7C4) hover above the water at different heights, wings catching amber light. A flat, pale grey granite (#A9A9A9) stone juts out over the pond's edge like a natural bench, its surface worn satin-smooth from years of use, sage-green (#8A9A5B) and burnt-orange (#CC5500) lichen clinging to its underside, the stone sitting empty beneath the banyan canopy receiving dappled light. A narrow path of hard-packed rust-red (#8B4513) earth leads from distant hazy village houses in the background toward the pond's edge, dry grass bordering the path on either side greening as it nears the waterline. Yellow mustard (#E1AD01) wildflowers and pale violet wood sorrel (#9B7ED8) line the eastern bank. No characters are present, the scene is a tranquil, expectant landscape holding its breath in the golden warmth. Pixar-style 3D, soft global illumination, polished cinematic quality. Color palette of warm amber, copper-gold, terracotta, emerald green, jade, tawny-gold, pale pink, and cerulean blue.",
